text: Map of the Falkland Islands showing Keppel Sound Keppel Sound (Spanish: Bahia de la Cruzada ) is a bay to the north of West Falkland in the Falkland Islands. Islands in/bordering the sound include Golding Island and Keppel Island. ==References== Category:West Falkland Category:Straits of the Falkland Islands Category:Bays of West Falkland
title: Keppel Sound
